 transaction reporting and transparency.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
There are several regulators, most of them can be found in any country:
 Banking supersvision (U.S: the Federal Reserve Bank), Insurance & Financial
 Services supervision, Capital market supervision, Anti-trust supervision.
