 T-note, T-bonds, TIPS.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
All treasuries are issued through a public bid and are traded through brokers
 on the secondary market.
 They are reinvestment, interest and inflation risk.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The FI securities are federally-related institutions (implicit) or government-sp
onsored enterprises (explicit).
\end_layout

